# 🚀 LIGTAS ULTRA-PERFORMANCE AI IGNORE
# Strictly enforced recursive blocking for maximum AI speed.

# ─── RECURSIVE DEPENDENCY BLOCK ───
**/node_modules/
**/node_modules/**
**/.next/
**/build/
**/.dart_tool/
**/out/

# ─── CLOUD & DB ARTIFCATS ───
.vercel/
.supabase/
.turbo/
.cache/
.npm/

# ─── ENV & SECRETS ───
.env*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key

# ─── SYSTEM & IDE JUNK ───
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea/
.expo/
.project
.DS_Store
*.tsbuildinfo
*.log

# ─── MEDIA & BINARIES (The Bloat) ───
**/assets/
**/public/icons/
**/public/images/
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.png
*.gif
*.svg
*.pdf
*.zip
*.mp4
*.exe
*.dll

# ─── WEB BRAND ASSETS (must be deployable) ───
!web/public/resqtrack-logo.jpg
!web/public/favicon.ico
!web/public/favicon.png
!web/public/apple-touch-icon.png
!web/public/icons/
!web/public/icons/**

# ─── TEMP/BACKUP ───
tmp/
temp/
backup/
*.bak
# ─── WINDOWS SYSTEM BLOCK (Fixes Scan Crashes) ───
System Volume Information/
WindowsApps/
$RECYCLE.BIN/
$Recycle.Bin/
Config.Msi/
Recovery/

